
To Install:
1) Install Django

2) Setup the pre-installed pyjamas:
    cd pyjamas-0.7/
    python bootstrap.py
    OR (if you will be using Pyjamas-Desktop)
    sudo python run_bootstrap_first_then_setup.py install


***** NOT WORKING YET ****
3) Setup Pyjamas-Desktop
    export PYTHONPATH=/Users/adzhigir/src/softchord/pyjamas-0.7/library/
**************************


To build and run:

1) Complile the front end to JavaScript and HTML:
    cd softchordapp/media/
    ./build.sh

2) Run the server:
    cd softchordapp/
    python manage.py runserver

3) Test it out:
    * In your browser, goto: http://127.0.0.1:8000/site_media/output/softchordapp.html

